Wow! All the way to the hard puzzles!
Nice work.

Santa asks you to do one last thing: Decrypt his hard drive.
His hard e is a really long string of text. When decoded, it will give
you a secret message.

Two things.
a) You’ll need to remove certain characters
b) After you do so, it will be in hexadecimal.

Expected result:
The final string of text.

Here’s your puzzle input.
